data.description: Gorgeous 5-bed, 3-bath home with pool in Redlands. Wood tile flooring throughout most of the home and exterior patio. Stunning kitchen boasting a pantry for storage, granite countertops, and a cooking island with a sink as well as a separate double sink. Formal dining and living rooms feature bay windows and crown molding. The family room offers a pool view. Laundry room with washer, dryer, and tub has a convenient outdoor access. Master bedroom has his and her closets; renovated 2021 master bathroom boasts a barn door, dual sinks, touch-light mirror, and separate tub/shower. Covered patio with tiled floors adds charm. Pool features heated spa, shed, concrete slab, and privacy fence. New A/C, hot water heater, impact windows/doors. Freshly painted in 2022, professionally landscaped.
